overview: A982 goes on a grand journey to get a crystal of unknown power... to the dismay of everyone. They all worry that A982 is younger than A983, and that he might be in great danger.  So, what do they do? They go on a grand adventure to warn A982 about the dangers the crystal might hold. But will it result in a bad ending? Or will A982 learn about the dangers he might face? Let's find out when the movie releases...
tagline: A grand adventure to find a little stickman.
title: A983 VS. A982 II
